data.description: Welcome to your dream starter home or investment in Cape Coral, built in 2017 with solid craftsmanship by LGI. This single-family haven offers not just a home, but a lifestyle—perfectly blending convenience, style, and room for growth. Inside you'll enjoy the open-concept design that flows out to the sprawling backyard. Enjoy modern comforts like the air conditioned garage, to a well-appointed kitchen that will inspire your inner chef. Here's where it gets even better: this gem sits on an expansive triple lot. Envision the unlimited possibilities—extend your living space, build a luxe outdoor kitchen, or create a tropical oasis complete with a pool and swaying palm trees. Your very own slice of paradise! Nestled in a friendly community, you’re within arm’s reach of top-rated schools and vibrant shopping centers. Whether you’re taking a quick trip to pick up groceries or planning a day of retail therapy, everything you need is just minutes away. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of Southwest Florida's magic at an unbeatable price.
